{"tid":1136073,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登大屠殺，殺盡天下連登仔！","createTime":"2019-05-02T18:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T18:34:06.000Z","uid":216132,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1684bf19fd7afd583bfb5d73d00eb3acc8c95327","tid":1136073,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:00:56.000Z","msg":"今日，香港最大嘅論壇 LIHKG 傳出咗一個驚人嘅消息。<br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔，朝早起身不約而同為返工起身，打開手機，即上連登。<br />\n<br />\n我諗任何人都諗唔到，置頂嘅標題竟然會係呢個：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一屆 LIHKG 大屠殺正式開始！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7avZbGX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7avZbGX.jpg&h=f084aa33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位連登會員！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋已經被強制參加連登大屠殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而冇account嘅香港人，亦都會獲贈一個連登會籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人人有份，永不落空<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲開始之前，首先講畀大家聽幾個規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港即時進入無政府狀態，任何法律都唔會生效<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果你獲得嘅負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />數量多於正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁恭喜你！你頭上會有一個懸賞，只要成功殺咗你，就可以獲得官方派發嘅虛擬膠幣！負評越多，派膠越多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 你可以用我哋嘅手機app 既掃描器，睇得出別人嘅總正/負數字！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 正評係需要付出膠幣作為代價。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 每人一開始都會有十個膠幣，而除咗殺人，係冇辦法用其他方法得到㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 手機冇電或者搵唔到食水？唔使擔心！只要你手上有膠幣，就可以上 LIHKG MALL 買到任何補給！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 祝大家殺人愉快！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG 營運團隊仝人敬上！"},{"pid":"565ba3197ce2d39130989b33817a9b58bcc3cd7b","tid":1136073,"uid":204916,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:02:07.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"08adadb602cffd62f701d14a3d580627bfc73d35","tid":1136073,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:03:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呀...黑痴！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"25ac0214721ff5f1b0165f6126cff63b6a5e8ef3","tid":1136073,"uid":10277,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MrGmqaQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrGmqaQ.gif&h=042376ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"014ec7676d96f584181e0a07d8da903d8f5908c3","tid":1136073,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:04:06.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"ea0111edb7b88ea228f84624d764d0cf38138f84","tid":1136073,"uid":197514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c1e034f7649f4ab3163318d6640bdfef3d84e7f","tid":1136073,"uid":10277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bv8jWhY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbv8jWhY.png&h=09c58c3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8bdd5edb5d6f02f680704a90bafdf7df2ffb58d","tid":1136073,"uid":147198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"太長 唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc653910f6e05eedd04f50e5f5e93fda681649ae","tid":1136073,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"「大家好，今天你陳嘉儀同你睇天氣。今天天氣唔錯呢，除左清晨下過幾陣驟雨之外，其餘時間都係陽光普照，而且有啲乾燥。因為一股乾燥既東北季候風，正為華南帶來普遍晴朗既天氣&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n天氣報告講嘅嘢一切如常，呢個唔通係連登想宣傳自己個新功能 LIHKG MALL 既營銷策略？<br />\n<br />\n呢個玩笑未免開得太大啊？<br />\n<br />\n我繼續碌落去睇其他留言，大部分人都抱住唔太相信嘅態度，但係亦有人cap圖，連登真係多咗 LIHKG MALL 同埋掃描器功能......<br />\n<br />\n愈向下碌，愈覺得唔對路。<br />\n<br />\n有人真係cap左圖，顯示自己打左格仔嘅屋企人頭頂上有數字。<br />\n<br />\n到底係photoshop出嚟定係現實？"},{"pid":"eb18a6ce1f1cac74c707c817b3dd5561ed5abd09","tid":1136073,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"e果巧少😂"},{"pid":"b54035fe55f4eaa723b7a8afe91c1cc54b503c8b","tid":1136073,"uid":10277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1A6Bj4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1A6Bj4.png&h=93450b66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2872c3ed3299f2c30c0785b401fca5d751c5d729","tid":1136073,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:19:27.000Z","msg":"開始有人提議：「不如負評曬啲五毛，負評平曬啲5p仔，等佢哋冇得再喺香港搞事！」<br />\n<br />\n有個人下面回覆，即刻扮假膠MK，獲得咗過千負評。<br />\n<br />\n睇咗一輪，發現自己好似浪費咗好多時間，都係時候要返工，於是就出咗門口。<br />\n<br />\n至於呢個大屠殺，我根本冇放喺心上。<br />\n<br />\n喺如常塞車嘅紅隧，我再次打開 LIHKG app ，想睇下呢個新開嘅商店功能，到底何方神聖。<br />\n<br />\n到底會唔會好似hktv mall咁要買夠400蚊先送貨？<br />\n<br />\n我隨便㩒咗一包薯片，價格係一個膠幣。<br />\n<br />\n我撳完付款，並冇轉跳到其他頁面，冇信用卡，冇入屋企地址。<br />\n<br />\n佢只係話我完成咗購買，唔通呢個係一個bug？<br />\n<br />\n我眼前，忽然出現咗一包薯片，跌落喺我嘅雙手之間。<br />\n<br />\n完全係無預警咁憑空出現。"},{"pid":"8dba56e40f49fd4fa3d234eff143d215a62a9240","tid":1136073,"uid":216132,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"我完全目定口呆咁望住手中嘅薯片，唔知畀咩反應好，現實根本冇可能有物件憑空出現呀嘛？<br />\n<br />\n根本唔需要討論科學嘅層面，都已經知道嘅事實！<br />\n<br />\n巴士上面，忽然大家嘅手機此起彼落咁響起。<br />\n<br />\n「蘋果日報特別新聞-只有成為壹會員先可以閱讀<br />\n<br />\n香港懷疑發生一單兇殺案，死者陳xx，懷疑因為於網上論壇被大量負評，一名37歲休班警員響應論壇活動，將其槍殺與單位內，疑犯仍然在逃。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示現正徹查事件，並且要求論壇官方立刻將該活動撤銷。該論壇的營運商至今未有回覆。網絡安全及科技罪案調查科表示，該論壇為目前香港最大論壇，發佈如此消息...」"},{"pid":"e71ad2e4aac32165a622451e16f9f8ea5a94d5eb","tid":1136073,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EE3cwZ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEE3cwZ7.png&h=9bfb1c42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"985838220c22302fe60d8ecee048c677dcd4e506","tid":1136073,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:32:53.000Z","msg":"開錯台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416b146c050ec5b08e53a7547cc062dcb2d2dc72","tid":1136073,"uid":167330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T18:34:06.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪應該開喺講故台？"}]}